  <brief_title>Cap Assisted Upper Endoscopy to Visualize the Major Duodenal Papilla</brief_title>
  <acronym>Kappa-I</acronym>
  <official_title>The Use of Cap Assisted Forward Viewing Esophagogastroduodenoscopy to Examine the Major Duodenal Papilla</official_title>
